lyrics:
[Verse]
In the depths of night, the rhythm takes control
Liquid melodies flowing, stirring my soul
A pulsating beat, it ignites my desire
Drum and bass liquid, takes me higher and higher

[Chorus]
Smooth as a river, it flows through my veins
Drum and bass liquid, erasing all my pains
Immersed in the vibe, I surrender, let go
This sonic embrace, sets my spirit aglow
style: psychedelic, experimental, very fast, growling, Black metal
